@startuml
title UC02 - Login Logout Sequence
actor User
participant "Web UI" as UI
participant "Auth API" as API
participant "Auth Service" as Svc
database "DB" as DB
User -> UI : Submit login form
UI -> API : POST /auth/login
API -> Svc : authenticate(email,password)
Svc -> DB : find user by email
DB --> Svc : user / not found
alt success
  Svc --> API : session/token
  API --> UI : 200 OK
  UI --> User : Redirect
else failure
  API --> UI : 401/403
  UI --> User : Show error
end
User -> UI : Logout
UI -> API : POST /auth/logout
API --> UI : session cleared
@enduml
